Prerequisites:
Minecraft Forge
Minecraft Coder Pack 7.2
Minecraft 1.3.2
http://www.minecraft.net

Setup:
Download official Minecraft launcher.
Run Minecraft once to download .minecraft directory

Download Minecraft Coder Pack 7.2 and extract somewhere
Download Minecraft Forge and extract forge directory into mcp base directory

copy bin/ and resources/ directories from .minecraft directory into jars/ directory in mcp base dir

Run forge install script.

clone Bookcase project into src/minecraft/